WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.400
My Works
Manage saved works, select active projects and continue writing.

2
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:12.900
Step 1 of 9
Menu returns to the main menu.

3
00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:19.399
Step 2 of 9
Create Empty Profile creates a blank work profile.

4
00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:25.899
Step 3 of 9
New Work opens the new work wizard.

5
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:32.399
Step 4 of 9
Search filters works by title, field or supervisor.

6
00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:38.899
Step 5 of 9
A project card contains type, title, date and action buttons.

7
00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:45.399
Step 6 of 9
Other cards represent saved or unfinished works.

8
00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:51.899
Step 7 of 9
A completed card shows title, field and supervisor.

9
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:58.399
Step 8 of 9
Select for Generation chooses the work as the active profile.

10
00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:04.900
Step 9 of 9
Continue Work, Open and Edit continue, open and modify the work.

11
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:11.400
Module explained
The user knows where to find the module, which parts to use and how to continue working.
